<plot>Another summer comedy compilation show, this program featured pilots for shows that had not been selected as part of the 1978 fall season, reruns of shows from earlier seasons, and a set of comedy skits by comic veteran Harvey Korman. Also included in the mix was a live-action version of the Archie comic strip, highlighting the antics of the gang from Riverdale High.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?019818</url></doc>
